  "detailed_description": "<h1>ROADMAP</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/533c698fd6c0cf8d10c0df88b09926ae.avif?t=1761937026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras_big/533c698fd6c0cf8d10c0df88b09926ae.avif?t=1761937026 width=800 height=430 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/20eb1fa6b0e28b98f7dc001722f856eb.poster.avif?t=1761937026\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/20eb1fa6b0e28b98f7dc001722f856eb.webm?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/20eb1fa6b0e28b98f7dc001722f856eb.mp4?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>About This Game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the eerie, endless corridors of the Backrooms in this intense multiplayer horror experience. With online co-op support for up to 7 players, you and your friends must survive the unsettling labyrinth, solve mysterious puzzles, and evade unspeakable horrors lurking in the shadows.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/744e5c7ea2846ff66f21a8d831d9cb08.poster.avif?t=1761937026\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/744e5c7ea2846ff66f21a8d831d9cb08.webm?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/744e5c7ea2846ff66f21a8d831d9cb08.mp4?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic Graphics & Environments:</strong> Immerse yourself in the Backrooms with stunning visuals and atmospheric detail.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Human Eye Focus Mechanic:</strong> A unique camera system mimics human eye focus — objects you're looking at become crystal clear, enhancing immersion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In-Game Pranks:</strong> Slap your friends or perform funny actions to lighten the tension — if only for a moment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer Survival:</strong> Split up or stick together — teamwork and communication are your lifelines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Horror Atmosphere:</strong> Dynamic lighting and detailed environments plunge you into forgotten rooms and impossible spaces.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terrifying Enemies:</strong> Each monster has distinct behaviors and hunts you relentlessly. Stay quiet, hide, and trust your instincts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 Challenging Levels:</strong> From claustrophobic halls to vast eerie areas, every level offers new horrors. Expect regular updates and new levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Co-op Puzzles & Escape Mechanics:</strong> Find keys, solve riddles, unlock exits — but danger lurks at every turn.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do You Have What It Takes?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/80ef0eed7fd181ad1029fcbb89d2f64a.poster.avif?t=1761937026\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/80ef0eed7fd181ad1029fcbb89d2f64a.webm?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/80ef0eed7fd181ad1029fcbb89d2f64a.mp4?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival demands strategy, stealth, and nerves of steel. Stay close to your team  or risk being lost forever. The Backrooms don't care how many survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready. Escape is possible but only together.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/54d3fdea15b0a339897dcdc3b16ae310.poster.avif?t=1761937026\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/54d3fdea15b0a339897dcdc3b16ae310.webm?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/54d3fdea15b0a339897dcdc3b16ae310.mp4?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/20eb1fa6b0e28b98f7dc001722f856eb.poster.avif?t=1761937026\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/20eb1fa6b0e28b98f7dc001722f856eb.webm?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/20eb1fa6b0e28b98f7dc001722f856eb.mp4?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>About This Game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the eerie, endless corridors of the Backrooms in this intense multiplayer horror experience. With online co-op support for up to 7 players, you and your friends must survive the unsettling labyrinth, solve mysterious puzzles, and evade unspeakable horrors lurking in the shadows.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/744e5c7ea2846ff66f21a8d831d9cb08.poster.avif?t=1761937026\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/744e5c7ea2846ff66f21a8d831d9cb08.webm?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/744e5c7ea2846ff66f21a8d831d9cb08.mp4?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic Graphics & Environments:</strong> Immerse yourself in the Backrooms with stunning visuals and atmospheric detail.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Human Eye Focus Mechanic:</strong> A unique camera system mimics human eye focus — objects you're looking at become crystal clear, enhancing immersion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In-Game Pranks:</strong> Slap your friends or perform funny actions to lighten the tension — if only for a moment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer Survival:</strong> Split up or stick together — teamwork and communication are your lifelines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Horror Atmosphere:</strong> Dynamic lighting and detailed environments plunge you into forgotten rooms and impossible spaces.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terrifying Enemies:</strong> Each monster has distinct behaviors and hunts you relentlessly. Stay quiet, hide, and trust your instincts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 Challenging Levels:</strong> From claustrophobic halls to vast eerie areas, every level offers new horrors. Expect regular updates and new levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Co-op Puzzles & Escape Mechanics:</strong> Find keys, solve riddles, unlock exits — but danger lurks at every turn.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do You Have What It Takes?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/80ef0eed7fd181ad1029fcbb89d2f64a.poster.avif?t=1761937026\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/80ef0eed7fd181ad1029fcbb89d2f64a.webm?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/80ef0eed7fd181ad1029fcbb89d2f64a.mp4?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival demands strategy, stealth, and nerves of steel. Stay close to your team  or risk being lost forever. The Backrooms don't care how many survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready. Escape is possible but only together.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/54d3fdea15b0a339897dcdc3b16ae310.poster.avif?t=1761937026\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/54d3fdea15b0a339897dcdc3b16ae310.webm?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396740/extras/54d3fdea15b0a339897dcdc3b16ae310.mp4?t=1761937026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
